```markdown
# TaskMaster - Project Management SaaS

## Project Type
Full-stack Next.js 14 application with App Router and server actions

## Tech Stack
- Framework: Next.js 14 (App Router), TypeScript, React 18
- Styling: Tailwind CSS, Shadcn UI components
- Database: PostgreSQL 15 with Drizzle ORM
- Auth: NextAuth.js v5
- Deployment: Vercel

## Installed Puerto Plugins
- frontend-developer (component-builder, state-architect, style-implementer)
- api-developer (endpoint-builder, auth-implementer)
- database-architect (schema-designer, migration-manager, query-optimizer)

## Automatic Task Routing

### Frontend
WHEN creating components → AUTOMATICALLY invoke frontend-developer:component-builder
WHEN implementing client state → AUTOMATICALLY invoke frontend-developer:state-architect

### Backend
WHEN creating API routes → AUTOMATICALLY invoke api-developer:endpoint-builder
WHEN creating server actions → AUTOMATICALLY invoke api-developer:endpoint-builder
WHEN implementing auth → AUTOMATICALLY invoke api-developer:auth-implementer

### Database
WHEN designing schemas → AUTOMATICALLY invoke database-architect:schema-designer
WHEN creating migrations → AUTOMATICALLY invoke database-architect:migration-manager
WHEN optimizing queries → AUTOMATICALLY invoke database-architect:query-optimizer

## Project Patterns

### File Structure (App Router)
```
app/
├── (auth)/            # Auth group
│   ├── login/
│   └── signup/
├── (dashboard)/       # Protected group
│   ├── projects/
│   └── tasks/
├── api/              # API routes
└── actions/          # Server actions
components/
├── ui/               # Shadcn components
└── [feature]/        # Feature components
```

### Component Patterns
- Use Shadcn UI components as base
- Server Components by default
- Client Components only when needed (mark with 'use client')
- Co-locate components with routes when route-specific

### Server Actions Pattern
```typescript
// app/actions/tasks.ts
'use server';

import { revalidatePath } from 'next/cache';
import { auth } from '@/lib/auth';

export async function createTask(formData: FormData) {
  const session = await auth();
  if (!session) throw new Error('Unauthorized');

  // Business logic

  revalidatePath('/dashboard/tasks');
}
```

### Database Patterns
- Drizzle ORM for type-safe queries
- Schemas in: `db/schema.ts`
- Migrations in: `db/migrations/`
- Use transactions for multi-table operations
- Index frequently queried columns

## Domain Knowledge
- Multi-tenancy: All data scoped to workspaceId
- Permissions: Role-based (owner, admin, member)
- Real-time: Use Supabase Realtime for live updates
- Webhooks: Stripe for billing, Slack for notifications
- Data retention: Soft delete with 30-day retention before hard delete
```

</details>

